<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹lyk ạ̉bkr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹lyk ạ̉bkr .. yạ ạ̹lhy .. ʿṭsẖt lk nfsy
 kạ̉rḍiⁿ yạbsẗ .. lạ mạʾ fyhạ .. hkdẖạ nḥwk qlby
 klt ʿynạya .. mn ạntẓạrk .. wtʿbt mn ṣrạkẖy
 (kktẖrẗ mrạḥmk .. ạltft ạ̹lyã .. bḥq kẖlạṣk njny)2
 2- ạqtrb ạ̹lyã .. fkny .. ạ̉srʿ ạ̹ly̱ mʿwnty
 ḥbạl ạlhạwyẗ .. ạ̉ṭbqt ʿlyã .. tʿbt mn sẖqạwty
 lạ tṭrḥny .. mn ạ̉mạmk .. wjhk lạ tḥjbh ʿny
 (ạ̹lyk ạ̉kẖṭạ̉t .. wạlsẖr ṣnʿt .. ạ̉lạ tʿwd ạ̉nt ftḥyny)2
 3- ạ̉ḥtạj ldmk .. yạ ạ̹lhy .. lystr kẖṭyty
 ḥmạmạaⁿ mqdsaⁿạ .. ḥty̱ ạlʿẓạm .. ạrḥmny wạnhḍ qlby
 ʿnd ṣlybk .. ạrsl nạrk .. ltḥrq kl ậtẖạmy
 (ạ̉tạ̉ml fy ḥbk .. fy ṣdq wʿdk .. ạ̉rạk ạ̹lhy tmsḥ dmʿty)2
 4- ạḥbk yạ ạ̹lhy .. yạ qwty .. mbạrkuⁿ yạ ṣkẖrty
 ḥmạyty sndy .. mljạ̉y mtkly .. ạ̉nt rby mnyr ẓlmty
 ạ̉ḥyạ lmjdk .. lṭwʿ ạ̉mrk .. lạ bqwty bl brwḥk
 (ạsẖʿlny bnạrk .. lạ̉bqy̱ qrbk .. ḍʿfy yrfʿ bsẖkẖṣk)2</lyrics>
